OL,4,Cpensioner #42,000 for minor garden work
OL,6,FShaw was arrested and subsequently
OL,7,Fcharged with fraud by false
OL,8,Frepresentation.
OL,10,FThe 34-year-old, of Tolney Lane,
OL,11,FNewark, and formerly of Hilton,
OL,12,Fadmitted the charge and appeared at
OL,13,FDerby Crown Court for sentencing on 23
OL,14,FMay.
OL,16,FHe was jailed for three years and four
OL,17,Fmonths.
