OL,3,CJail for man who fraudulently charged
OL,4,Cpensioner #42,000 for minor garden work
OL,6,FPC Emily Carnan, who led the
OL,7,Finvestigation, said: "This was a
OL,8,Fdespicable and targeted attack on a
OL,9,Fvulnerable elderly man.
OL,11,F"Shaw took money from the victim many
OL,12,Ftimes, knowing that because of his
OL,13,Fdementia, he couldn't remember paying
OL,14,Fhim previously.
OL,16,F"Over the course of just a few months
OL,17,Fhe took a huge amount of money for
OL,18,Fwork which was not only vastly over
OL,19,Fpriced but also incredibly sub
OL,20,Fstandard.
